Our research project titled "Investigating soil water and nitrogen interactive effects on biological nitrogen fixation using remote sensing" has received funding support from Manitoba Pulse & Soybean Growers (MPSG) (2026 Apr - 2028 Dec)! 
<br>
This project is in collaboration with Dr. Dilshan Benaragama from the Department of Plant Science, University of Manitoba and Dr. Kevin Baron from Solum Valley Biosciences.
<br>
We acknowledge MPSG's support and look forward to generating meaningful findings and practical contributions.
